VERBOSE-COMMON-NEXT: RISCV_GOT_LOAD : Cannot relax 4 bytes for symbol 'sym_zero'
VERBOSE-COMMON-NEXT: RISCV_GOT_LOAD : Deleting 4 bytes for symbol 'sym_cli_pos'
